huge pressure for this exhibition.

694
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:14,590
That message was sent

695
00:36:14,590 --> 00:36:16,590
just to get more guests

696
00:36:16,590 --> 00:36:18,000
to show up and support me.

697
00:36:18,190 --> 00:36:19,590
It was sent out in bulk.

698
00:36:19,590 --> 00:36:20,480
But you

699
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:22,377
were the only one
I came to invite in person.

700
00:36:22,377 --> 00:36:23,710
Doesn't that show how I feel?

701
00:36:27,666 --> 00:36:29,880
Nana, you'll come
to my exhibition tomorrow, right?

702
00:36:30,030 --> 00:36:31,030
Drive safe, please.

703
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:38,960
Zhang, go settle the bill.

704
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:40,222
Have the car come pick me up.

705
00:36:43,840 --> 00:36:44,680
Lu Feng.

706
00:36:47,320 --> 00:36:48,320
Do you remember me?

707
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:50,800
You are...

708
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:52,630
We met at Tianguang Market.

709
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:53,960
Where?

710
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:55,480
We were rowing on the river.

711
00:36:55,670 --> 00:36:56,510
You even...

712
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,160
Nice to meet you.

713
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:01,160
Nice to meet you.

714
00:37:02,710 --> 00:37:04,230
My friend and I wanted to talk to you.

715
00:37:04,230 --> 00:37:05,230
Do you have a moment?

716
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:06,670
My car's here.

717
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:08,066
I've got an exhibition tomorrow.

718
00:37:08,111 --> 00:37:09,480
Add my assistant on WeChat.

719
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,644
We'll get in touch later.

720
00:37:11,190 --> 00:37:12,550
No, wait.

721
00:37:12,550 --> 00:37:13,710
Sorry, Mr. Lu is in a hurry.

722
00:37:13,710 --> 00:37:15,044
Let's exchange contact details.

723
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:17,760
Sorry about that.

724
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:20,720
Don't forget.

725
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:26,030
Why did he act like
he didn't know me at all?

726
00:37:27,688 --> 00:37:29,360
He definitely doesn't remember you.

727
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:33,360
People who leave Tianguang Market
lose their memories.

728
00:37:33,630 --> 00:37:34,670
That really happens?

729
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,550
Tianguang Market is a time rift.

730
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:37,420
Strictly speaking,

731
00:37:37,420 --> 00:37:40,110
what happens there
doesn't belong to any timeline.

732
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,590
But I went there, too.

733
00:37:43,590 --> 00:37:44,711
Why didn't I forget anything?

734
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:46,550
You entered through Yashe.

735
00:37:46,577 --> 00:37:49,000
That's different from people
who wander in by accident.

736
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:52,400
Do you think he'll contact us?

737
00:37:52,533 --> 00:37:54,070
If you're waiting for him to reach out,

738
00:37:54,070 --> 00:37:55,480
you'll probably be disappointed.

739
00:37:55,480 --> 00:37:56,480
What do we do?

740
00:37:57,022 --> 00:37:58,400
There's nothing we can do.

741
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,710
We came all this way

742
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:01,550
for nothing?

743
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:02,920
Since we're already here,

744
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:03,840
take a look around.

745
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:13,510
Big cities really are different.

746
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:15,800
Huayang has changed so much.

747
00:38:20,150 --> 00:38:20,990
Bizhi.

748
00:38:22,440 --> 00:38:23,320
The future...

749
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:24,670
What's it like?

750
00:38:25,030 --> 00:38:27,190
Is it like sci-fi movies,

751
00:38:27,190 --> 00:38:28,590
