759
00:38:43,230 --> 00:38:44,110
Do you own a place?

760
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,510
How many rooms?

761
00:38:45,510 --> 00:38:46,350
Is it...

762
00:38:51,510 --> 00:38:52,760
I have one room.

763
00:38:54,440 --> 00:38:55,840
There's a bed,

764
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:57,630
