766
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,120
That's it?

767
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:08,550
Bare walls and nothing else.

768
00:39:12,230 --> 00:39:14,440
But technology lets me
have anything I want.

769
00:39:17,190 --> 00:39:18,550
That still sounds boring.

770
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:20,710
I think the present is more interesting.

771
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:22,230
It feels alive.

772
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:23,720
Look.

773
00:39:24,030 --> 00:39:25,590
I can scroll on my phone.

774
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:28,630
All these cats and dogs,

